            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-primary-700)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" class="mb-4"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0118 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Government Data on Every Destination Your Team Visits</h3>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">Real-time intelligence from 5 government sources -- not a Google search. NOAA weather data, CDC health advisories, USGS seismic activity, and two international humanitarian agencies. Risk scored with Monte Carlo simulation so you understand probability, not just possibility.</p>
