            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-foreground)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" class="mb-4"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"/></svg>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Audit-Ready Documentation for Your Insurance Carrier and Board</h3>
